com.rhizospherejs.gwt.rebind
Class BridgeCapabilities

java.lang.Object
  com.rhizospherejs.gwt.rebind.BridgeCapabilities

public class BridgeCapabilities
extends java.lang.Object

Enumerates the supported mapping capabilities between Java types and equivalent Rhizosphere types for the purpose of converting POJOs into custom tailored JavaScriptObjects usable as Rhizosphere models.

JSO_BUILDER_CLASS enumerates methods to assemble a Rhizosphere model from Java values and types. This class analyzes JSO_BUILDER_CLASS and builds a mapping between a Java type and an associated method that can port values of that type onto a Rhizosphere model.

Author:
battlehorse@google.com (Riccardo Govoni)
